products.title: ASUS TUF Gaming GeForce GTX 1660 Super Overclocked 6GB Edition HDMI DP DVI Gaming Graphics Card (TUF-GTX1660S-O6G-GAMING)
features: Powered by NVIDIA Turing with 1845 MHz Boost Clock, 1408 CUDA cores and overclocked 6GB GDDR6 memory in a 2. 7 slot form Factor
Space-grade lubricant brings the durability of dual Ball bearings to quieter Sleeve bearing designs.
Gpu Tweak II makes monitoring performance and streaming in real time easier than ever, and includes additional software like Game Booster, XSplit Gamecaster, WTFast and quantumcloud
Tuf compatibility testing runs cards through a suite of tests to ensure TUF Gaming motherboards, chassis, and other TUF Gaming Alliance components work together flawlessly
Auto-extreme technology delivers premium quality and reliability using an automated manufacturing process
products.description: Powered by NVIDIA Turing, the Asus TUF Gaming GeForce GTX 1660 Super delivers legendary durability and performance Featuring auto extreme manufacturing technology. The overclocked 6GB GDDR6 memory is cooled by dual-ball Bearing fans housed in a shroud designed to match Asus TUF Gaming motherboards and TUF Gaming Alliance products.
